channel.title: PortForward Help

item.title: PortForward Help
item.dc:creator: @TheHolyGrail TheHolyGrail
item.description:
@TheHolyGrail wrote:

Ethernet isn’t a router. :rolleyes:

Go to your command promp and type: ipconfig

Push enter, and it will tell you your Ip address. Type it into your url bar and it should go to your router.

Hope I helped.

EDIT:

My 100th post, cheers to Senior Member.
